<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CASE_STUDY // CHLOE_ART - Terminal</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --rush-white: #ffffff;
            --rush-fuchsia: #ff00ff;
            --bg-dark: #050505;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            color: #d1d5db;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Scanline Overlay */
        body::after {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.1), rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 2px);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .terminal-border {
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Data HUD Brackets */
        .bracket::before, .bracket::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 12px; height: 12px;
            border-color: var(--rush-white);
            border-style: solid;
        }
        .bracket-tl::before { top: -1px; left: -1px; border-width: 2px 0 0 2px; }
        .bracket-br::after { bottom: -1px; right: -1px; border-width: 0 2px 2px 0; }

        .glow-white { text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.5); color: #fff; }
        .fuchsia-text { color: var(--rush-fuchsia); }
        
        .code-window {
            background: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.9);
            border-left: 2px solid var(--rush-fuchsia);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-4 md:p-10">

    <header class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-start mb-16">
        <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
                <a href="index.html" class="text-[10px] border border-white/20 px-3 py-1 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all">RETURN_TO_CORE</a>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-white/30 tracking-[0.4em]">PROJECT_ID: 002-CHLOE</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white">Project_Analysis // <span class="glow-white">ART_GALLERY_ENGINE</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:block text-right">
            <span class="block text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase">Production Status</span>
            <span class="block text-[10px] fuchsia-text">LIVE_ON_NETWORK</span>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
            <div class="terminal-border bracket bracket-tl p-1 mb-10 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618005182384-a83a8bd57fbe?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" 
                     alt="Chloe Portfolio Preview" 
                     class="w-full opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700">
                <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-black/80 px-3 py-1 border border-white/10 text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">
                    UI_Capture_V1.0
                </div>
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white italic tracking-tighter uppercase leading-tight mb-6">
                CHLOE'S <span class="text-transparent" style="-webkit-text-stroke: 1px #fff;">ART</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl border-l-2 border-fuchsia-600 pl-6 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                Designed and developed a high-performance, responsive portfolio for a digital illustrator. Engineered to showcase high-resolution artwork through a <span class="text-white">minimalist, content-first</span> professional interface.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-8">
            <div class="terminal-border p-6 bg-white/5">
                <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-fuchsia-500 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-6 border-b border-white/10 pb-2">Technical Execution</h3>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold block mb-1">Dynamic Grid Engine</span>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">CSS Grid with auto-fill logic for seamless 4K to Mobile scaling.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold block mb-1">Custom Lightbox Module</span>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">Vanilla JavaScript module for distraction-free artwork inspection.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold block mb-1">Communication Funnel</span>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">Gmail Compose API + Discord Community bridge for streamlined commissions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="terminal-border p-6 bracket bracket-br">
                <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4">Tech_Stack</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span class="bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-[9px] text-white font-bold border border-white/10">HTML5_SEMANTIC</span>
                    <span class="bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-[9px] text-white font-bold border border-white/10">CSS3_GRID</span>
                    <span class="bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-[9px] text-white font-bold border border-white/10">VANILLA_JS</span>
                    <span class="bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-[9px] text-white font-bold border border-white/10">DOM_MANIPULATION</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-12 mt-10">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-1 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(255,0,255,0.05)]">
                <div class="code-window p-8">
                    <div class="text-[9px] fuchsia-text mb-2">// OPTIMIZATION</div>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter mb-2">99% LIGHTSPEED</div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] opacity-50 uppercase">Zero external libraries used to maintain lightning-fast load times.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="code-window p-8">
                    <div class="text-[9px] fuchsia-text mb-2">// UX_STRATEGY</div>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter mb-2">SMOOTH_FLOW</div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] opacity-50 uppercase">Single-page architecture with custom anchor point navigation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="code-window p-8">
                    <div class="text-[9px] fuchsia-text mb-2">// ACCESSIBILITY</div>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter mb-2">SEO_READY</div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] opacity-50 uppercase">Fully semantic structure for search engine optimization.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-20 py-10 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center opacity-40">
        <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em]">Dev: Damion Thomasson // Build_2026</div>
        <a href="#" class="text-[10px] font-bold border-b border-white/20 hover:border-fuchsia-500 transition-colors">INITIALIZE_LIVE_PREVIEW</a>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
